{"status":200,"code":1000,"message":null,"timestamp":"1762173532302","path":null,"data":{"id":1594,"title":"Manulife:推出「財摯傳承保障計劃」&「財摯家傳保障計劃」及推廣優惠","type":"PRODUCT_PROMOTION","time":1675652753776,"tags":["宏利保險"],"content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">致合作夥伴：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>宏利香港</strong>於<strong><span style=\"color: #169179;\">2023年2月6日</span></strong>誠意推出整付保費的<strong><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">「財摯傳承保障計劃」及「財摯家傳保障計劃」</span></strong>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 一、<span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">「財摯傳承保障計劃」</span>產品特點：</strong></span></p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">提供穩定增長及提升長期儲蓄的潛在回報</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">提供首日退保價值高達整付保費之80.05%以作保費融資</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">提供終期紅利鎖定權益/保單分拆/意外身故保障/更改受保人及後備受保人等服務</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 二、<span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">「財摯家傳保障計劃」</span>產品特點：</strong></span></p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">助您積累財富，提升長期儲蓄的潛在回報。計劃更特設遞增人壽保障，於指定名義金額下無需醫療核保</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">提供首日退保價值高達整付保費之77%以作保費融資</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">提供終期紅利鎖定權益/保單分拆/意外身故保障</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 三、推廣優惠：</strong></span></p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #169179;\">推廣期：2023年2月6日-2023年3月31日(包括首尾兩天)</span></strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">投保<strong><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">「財摯傳承保障計劃」及「財摯家傳保障計劃」，</span></strong>可享<strong><span style=\"color: #e67e23;\">高達8%保費折扣優惠</span></strong></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2023-02-06/755446a6f2ba4d7f9206b58235a764ac.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 詳情請參閱附件。</span></p>","attachments":[{"fileName":"NewsFlash-TC.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2023-02-06/d03a6a66ca124733a29cb4e4227e5c50.pdf","uploadTime":1675649878390,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"NewsFlash-EN.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2023-02-06/13852d3a579241b0997f313368f89694.pdf","uploadTime":1675649881225,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"新產品之推廣優惠.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2023-02-06/232fd103c23646fab3dcda48e528e7e8.pdf","uploadTime":1675649884001,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null}],"companyCode":"MANULIFE","companyName":"宏利保險","productCodes":["MANULIFE:PSV","MANULIFE:PPS"],"productNames":["財摯傳承保障計劃","財摯家傳保障計劃"],"companyCodes":["MANULIFE"],"companyNames":["宏利保險"],"startEffectiveDate":1675647739988,"endEffectiveDate":1680226940004,"effective":false}}